              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25448393/" class="">第32页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/manstars/" class=" " title="风之子">风之子</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25448393">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">学徒制和雇佣制的区别是劳动力的商品化；以饥饿迫使劳动力商品化（可联系《饥荒与政治》）</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-28 23:18</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                学徒制和雇佣制的区别是劳动力的商品化；以饥饿迫使劳动力商品化（可联系《饥荒与政治》）
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25448393/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
